daily_txn=data.groupby('transaction_date')['transaction_id'].count()
daily_sales=data.groupby('transaction_date')['sales'].sum()

plt.figure(figsize=(12,6))
sns.lineplot(x=daily_txn.index, y=daily_txn.values, marker='o', color='#C8A2F0')
plt.title('Daily Transaction Count')
plt.xlabel('Date')
plt.ylabel('Number of Transactions')


plt.figure(figsize=(12,6))
sns.lineplot(x=daily_sales.index, y=daily_sales.values, marker='o', color='purple')
plt.title('Daily Sales')
plt.xlabel('Date')
plt.ylabel('Sales ($)')
plt.show()
In [14]:
hourly_sales = data.groupby('hour')['sales'].sum()
hourly_txn = data.groupby('hour')['transaction_id'].count()

plt.figure(figsize=(12,6))
sns.lineplot(x=hourly_sales.index, y=hourly_sales.values, marker='o', color=cm.Oranges(0.7))
plt.title('Hourly Sales Trend')
plt.xlabel('Hour of Day')
plt.ylabel('Sales ($)')

plt.figure(figsize=(12,6))
sns.barplot(x=hourly_txn.index, y=hourly_txn.values, palette=sns.color_palette("inferno", len(hourly_txn)))
plt.title('Transactions by Hour')
plt.xlabel('Hour of Day')
plt.ylabel('Transaction Count')
plt.show()

In [16]:
top5_cat = data.groupby('product_category')['sales'].sum().sort_values(ascending=False).head(5)

plt.figure(figsize=(8,8))
wedges, texts, autotexts = plt.pie(
    top5_cat,
    autopct='%1.1f%%',
    colors=sns.color_palette("viridis", 5),
    startangle=140,
    textprops={'color':'white', 'weight':'bold', 'fontsize':12})
plt.legend(wedges, top5_cat.index, title="Categories", loc="center left", bbox_to_anchor=(1, 0, 0.5, 1))
plt.title('Top 5 % Product Categories by Sales')
plt.show()
In [17]:
top5_cat = data.groupby('product_category')['sales'].sum().sort_values(ascending=False).head(5).reset_index()

plt.figure(figsize=(10,6))
sns.set_style("whitegrid")

bar = sns.barplot(x='sales', y='product_category', data=top5_cat,
                  palette=sns.color_palette("plasma", 5))


for i, (sales) in enumerate(top5_cat['sales']):
    bar.text(sales + max(top5_cat['sales'])*0.01, i, f"${sales:,.2f}", va='center', fontsize=11)

plt.title('Top 5 Product Categories by Sales', fontsize=16, weight='bold')
plt.xlabel('Sales ($)')
plt.ylabel('Category')
plt.show()

data['month'] = data['transaction_date'].dt.to_period('M')
monthly_sales = data.groupby('month')['sales'].sum()


plt.figure(figsize=(12,6))
sns.lineplot(x=monthly_sales.index.astype(str), y=monthly_sales.values,
             marker='o', color=cm.Purples(0.7))
plt.title('Monthly Sales Trends')
plt.xlabel('Month')
plt.ylabel('Sales ($)')
plt.show()
